text: Sophie Lowe (born 5 June 1990) is an English-born Australian actress and singer-songwriter. She starred in Beautiful Kate, After the Dark, Adore, and Road Kill, and starred in the television series The Slap, Once Upon a Time in Wonderland, The Returned and The Beautiful Lie. ==References== ==Other websites== * * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Australian movie actors Category:Australian television actors Category:Australian singer- songwriters
